reviewText:
The menu selection was very poorly done, as it was hard to determine which one of the selections was being selected or to be played.

Only one of the three models was completely nude.

About one third of each video started without the model and each of the videos had about one and a half minute of credits, so two of the three videos showed about one and a half minute of the model in the video.

The longest video showed about five minutes of the model being covered with what I think was black light paints to show their colors. Most of the time was spent with the model covering her feet and legs, with about a minute with the model covering her upper body.
